_aChangeLog.text: Big boxes in bombsites have been replaced by biohazard tanks from CS:GO
Almost all wooden boxes are now a little bigger.
Added more lighting to B site
The window in bombsite B has become larger
Detailed terrain near the old Secret Entrance
Returned 2 windows on roof in Garage
T Boxes are returned to their original positions in Outside
The wood pallets are now breakable again in Bombsite A
Footsteps on bunch of boxes on Ramp now make wood sounds
Footsteps on pipes on T Roof now make metallic sounds
Removed gaps between boxes in Bombsite A and Outside
Fixed a couple of visual bugs

_sText:
Modification of de_nuke, which is based on CS:GO 2015 version of this map with some additions added by myself. 

The map is aimed at improving the gameplay of the map, but maintaining the CS:S atmosphere and aesthetics. Materials were used mostly from CS:S and HL2 assets. In addition to changes in geometry, the map has become lighter, HDR lighting has been smoothed out, ambient sounds have become quieter, bots now tell more accurate information about the position of the enemy.
